{"tid":25521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"實拍曱甴鑽耳窿　暖笠笠過冬","createTime":"2016-12-06T07:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T05:26:48.000Z","uid":39013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8fe15e00ab6b0bb75954df4d37dbff26449b814","tid":25521,"uid":39013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:17:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20161206/19856862\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20161206%2F19856862&d=u8WlpgPihxyMZGT20wMdJpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=ee092abd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20161206%2F19856862&h=4d07f677\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20161206/19856862</a><br />\n<br />\n溫暖的耳道竟然成為曱甴巢穴！湖南懷化巿的粟女士睡覺時耳朵突然劇痛，她估計有昆蟲鑽入耳朵，上周四起床後馬上到醫院求診。醫生用內窺鏡一看，發現粟女士耳朵內竟有一隻活活生的蟑螂，三對腳還不斷掙扎，粟女士當時亦感覺到蟑螂在耳內郁動，「耳朵一動時，還是有點痛！」<br />\n<br />\n懷化耳鼻喉醫院孟潔醫生表示，當日立即為粟女士麻醉，取出蟑螂，鉗了出來仍非常生猛；她提醒巿民床頭不要擺放食物，一旦有異物走入耳朵，不要嘗試自行挖出來，這樣或會把昆蟲或異物逼至耳道深處，可能令耳膜受傷，應該立即求醫，由醫生取出異物。　<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216d37e4e13253e7ba9014fc390df4fbcbd4d126","tid":25521,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:31:27.000Z","msg":"冬虫夏蝗"},{"pid":"95b5c42b3b762ffc67cff074e3f6572548ce327b","tid":25521,"uid":47301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:32:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冬虫夏蝗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ccb89f244915b17ec61ef2064d15e7bf845d3e","tid":25521,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:42:40.000Z","msg":"睇完隻耳仔都覺得有啲痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dadeebdeb31f6e648e1f4603aeee0c93eeb026b7","tid":25521,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"仲生既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc87e9c6f6c47016441649a2b7f500291d6f1f6","tid":25521,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲生既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食耳屎為生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f9f238bfda31398c7ae1f3850e4c5e9f7022cf","tid":25521,"uid":47301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:23:05.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"5c79f243ade00a62e55427dee73cc8d28b304ace","tid":25521,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T14:47:18.000Z","msg":"大耳隆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31edc7fcbb8a123c1b11fb34e2ae6bcaf1996fe8","tid":25521,"uid":10635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:26:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲生既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食耳屎為生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n差唔多乜都食， 靠耳內資源分分鐘夠過世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}